SUMMARY:Deadline: falía* AIR 2026 Artist Residency
DESCRIPTION:Summer artist residency in the mountain village of Lozio for in
 dividuals and collectives to create site-specific artworks\, with preferen
 ce for Land Art\, Street Art and participatory art. Residents receive a we
 ekly stipend\, shared accommodation\, workspace\, cultural activities and 
 co-production support\; selected artworks become donations to the Municipa
 lity.\n\nOrganisation: Associazione falía*\nLocation: Lozio\, Valle Camon
 ica\, Northern Italy\nAward: €70/week stipend (2 to 6 weeks) + shared ac
 commodation and workspace + co-production support\nDuration: 2 to 6 weeks 
 (summer)\n\nMore: https://falia-air.com/en/call-2026/
URL:https://falia-air.com/en/call-2026/
LOCATION:Lozio\, Valle Camonica\, Northern Italy
END:VEVENT
